  <article class="px-6 py-8 md:px-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">2025</p>

    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Burning a rome</h1>
    <section class="mt-14 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 px-6 py-6 tracking-wide">
      <p>
        I feel like burning a Rome<br />
        Just to speak in past tense<br />
        I feel like burning a Rome <br />
        In hopes of relevance.<br />
        
      </p>

      <p>
        And while Rome is burning<br />
Every house and every tree,<br />
And while Rome is burning<br />
There is a world besides me
      </p>

      <p>
        And in the glimming ashes<br />
The warmth of change and pain,<br />
In the glimming ashes<br />
I am awaiting for the rain.
      </p>

      <p>
        And as chaos sets for something new<br />
And I begin to return<br />
To the place reminding me of you<br />
